Package org.codehaus.mojo.servicedocgen

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Analyzer
    Analyzer contains the logic to analyze the services on byte-code and source-code level and create the according Descriptors.
    EscapeHelper
    Class with static methods for escaping strings in velocity templates.
    HelpMojo
    Display help information on servicedocgen-maven-plugin.
    Call mvn servicedocgen:help -Ddetail=true -Dgoal=<goal-name> to display parameter details.
    ServiceDocGenReport
    Maven Plugin to automatically generate documentation for services of the current project.
    ServiceDocGenTemplate
    ServiceDocGenTemplate is a template bean representing the templates passed into ServiceDocGenReport
    Util
    Utility class with static helper methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JavaScriptType
    Enum with types available in JavaScript.
